{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make zero hour contracts illegal",
        "additional_details": "I believe it should be mandatory for every company to guarantee each of its employees at least 16 hours of work per week. Too many managers abuse the power of the \u2018zero hour contract\u2019 and give their employees barely enough hours to afford food and clothing for their children \u2026 it is a joke!",
        "background": "The blanket phrase \u2018zero hour contract\u2019 allows many ways for companies to word \u2018we can\u2019t guarantee you any hours\u2019 and in my opinion it is a really abused system! Hard-working employees should be allowed the guarantee of a set number of hours per week in return for the work they provide.",
